<center><table border=0><tr><td><center><H2><font face=arial>Naked PKers...</font></H2></center>
<font face=arial size=2><b>Posted By:</b> <A HREF="/cgi-local/whois2.cgi?Kirista">Kirista</a><br>
<b>Posted On:</b> 2:51 p.m. 13/7/1999<br>
<b>Subject:</b> Naked PKers...<p>
<br><center><img src="http://www.everworld.net/pvpquest/images/divider.gif" width=452 height=22 border=0></center><BR></STRONG><FONT SIZE=2 color=#FFFFFF FACE=arial>
<P>I just realized something... after 15 levels bardness, it finally hit me--Bards are the perfect antiPK. Get a Pumice Shaped Orb (cancels magic), put your armor in the bank, take a cheapo minotaur axe and mem bellow, and go hunt the naked caster types. Sounds funny, eh?

<P>Well, shock! it works! You have nothing to lose, you have bellow, you can't be rooted, if you have that orb you can cancel DOT's, and you're faster than the casters. And if thats not enough, you can get a second bard (if ya read this Kirsta.. heh) and really kick some arse!
<P>It works. You just gotta be bold enough to stand up! And don't be stupid, if you have that oh-so-sweet item, bag it after a fight when you rest. Thats when they get you the most. All these problems can be easily avoided with a little thinking... and most Naked casters wont attack someone if they look like they're grouped--so even if you ARE soloing, rest next to a group for safety.
<P>I used to hate naked casters, but now I just laugh at them. Just take your time, think of the sweet revenge you can get, and do it. And dont be shy to get a group to gang rape em--they'll attack your honor, but then again what honor do they have? Why should you have honor and remorse for them when they didn't for you? Bah! don't fall into their mind tricks. Kill em, kill em all-like they said in the post below its mostly a character that funds another.
<P>-Kirista, Wood Elf Bard
</FONT></td></tr></table></P>
